  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><br /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/h5U7odw.png\" alt=\"FeatherLib Logo\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></strong></span></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px; font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\">FeatherLib</span><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">&nbsp;</span></h1 >\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>THIS MOD DOES NOTHING ON ITS OWN! Unless you need FeatherLib for another mod, do not install it.</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">See the&nbsp;<a title=\"Wiki\" href=\"https://github.com/SimplyCmd/FeatherLib/wiki\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Wiki</a>&nbsp;for information on features</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Adding to your project:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Please visit&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/SimplyCmd/FeatherLib/wiki\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/SimplyCmd/FeatherLib/wiki</a></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" width=\"310\" height=\"104\" /></span></p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-groovy-gradle position-relative\">&nbsp;</div>",
